        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3038882256" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1787182100487025320">A classic adventure story and early prototype of the spy/thriller genres. Plenty of action but none of it all that believable. This one wasn&apos;t really my style.</span>
  <span id="freeText1787182100487025320" style="display:none">A classic adventure story and early prototype of the spy/thriller genres. Plenty of action but none of it all that believable. This one wasn't really my style.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1787182100487025320" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

